items.Video_Title: Is COS The Best For Wardrobe Basics?
items.Video_Description:
You may have seen my recent UNIQLO video where I reviewed their clothing and gave my opinion on if I thought they were still the best for affordable basics. Well, a lot of you asked if I could do some other popular stores too, so I decided to do one of my favourites next, COS. 

Now COS is a little bit more expensive than UNIQLO, but not by much these days and I normally find their clothing fits a lot better, it’s more interesting and the quality is better too. It's been a while since I bought anything from COS, for no reason really. I just haven’t been buying much recently, but let’s see if they are still one of the best for basics out there. 

For this clothing haul, I picked up some t-shirts, outerwear, trousers and denim so I have all areas covered so it should give us a good idea on the quality.
